    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hirogami》是一款受日本传统折纸艺术启发的3D平台动作游戏，游戏中的世界随处可见精美的折纸造型，呈现出纸张独有的脆弱与自然之美。随着一段充满淡淡哀愁与神秘的自白，故事也就此展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变换形态，释放强大能力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索全新形态，游历世界各地，破解谜题，击败强敌。化身坚韧的犰狳，碾压障碍与敌人；化作强壮的大力猿，在藤蔓间穿行，猛击害兽；变为敏捷的青蛙，跃上曾无法触及的高地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9f0e421f6fe2d9f49fb1d48f3ba44cc6.poster.avif?t=1759228755\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9f0e421f6fe2d9f49fb1d48f3ba44cc6.webm?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9f0e421f6fe2d9f49fb1d48f3ba44cc6.mp4?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >守护美丽脆弱的折纸世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数据瘴气，一股由数字生物构成的强大力量侵入了纸艺大陆，破坏了延续已久的自然平衡。作为纸祀村的折纸大师、神秘的舞扇艺人，你将肩负起净化被瘴气感染的众生、重塑大地平衡的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/6e66c13bd48c3bd24227f5fae7994980.poster.avif?t=1759228755\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/6e66c13bd48c3bd24227f5fae7994980.webm?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/6e66c13bd48c3bd24227f5fae7994980.mp4?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索失落的秘密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索世界的各个角落，发现隐藏其中的秘密。展开为纸，乘着炽热气流升腾而上，或滑翔穿越致命陷阱；又或变身为纸飞机，飞越危机四伏的深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/419a04e7848f0177e72e72bc64df7c18.poster.avif?t=1759228755\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/419a04e7848f0177e72e72bc64df7c18.webm?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/419a04e7848f0177e72e72bc64df7c18.mp4?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将敌人击碎成纸片</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >折纸世界美丽却脆弱不堪，你必须凭借智慧来守护这片大陆。挥动浩的纸扇驱散瘴气，运用折纸能力击败强敌，不管是重击、挥拳，还是以毒攻敌，尽情发挥你的折纸才能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/18e606b53cd50d721d6271ad57b2f438.poster.avif?t=1759228755\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/18e606b53cd50d721d6271ad57b2f438.webm?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/18e606b53cd50d721d6271ad57b2f438.mp4?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >品味传统日式音乐韵律</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏音乐采用日式传统乐器与风格编曲，精心烘托《Hirogami》中的不同主题、角色与场景，打造温柔舒缓的沉浸式探索体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9fbfb0d977794b28cf30f5d3d4c65107.poster.avif?t=1759228755\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9fbfb0d977794b28cf30f5d3d4c65107.webm?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135840/extras/9fbfb0d977794b28cf30f5d3d4c65107.mp4?t=1759228755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入愿望单</h2>",
